appDisplayName: W&T COM Port Redirector Plug & Play
description:
Use W&T Com-Servers as virtual COM ports

Connect a Com-Server or a Web-IO with serial interface to the network 
and establish a virtual COM port on your system to make your serial 
applications network-capable.
